{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Happy October, everyone! We‚Äôre stoked, because October means‚Ä¶ Hacktoberfest!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"what-is-hacktoberfest"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#what-is-hacktoberfest","ariaLabel":"what is hacktoberfest permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"What is Hacktoberfest?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"‚ÄúHacktoberfest is a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com/faq"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"month-long celebration of open source software"}]},{"type":"text","value":" run by DigitalOcean in partnership with GitHub and Twilio.‚Äù"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hacktoberfest encourages open source contributions by motivating open source projects to create and label contributor-friendly issues, and pseudo-gamifying the participation of contributors. To take part:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com/sign_up/register"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"sign up"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to participate, and"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"submit five quality pull requests to public GitHub repositories (within the time frame of October 1‚Äì31)."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"So far, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues?q=is%3Aissue+sort%3Aupdated-desc+label%3AHacktoberfest+is%3Aclosed"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"30+ people have contributed"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to close out Gatsby Hacktoberfest issues, and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues?q=is%3Aissue+sort%3Aupdated-desc+label%3AHacktoberfest+is%3Aopen"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"there are 35 open"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Hacktoberfest issues, with more on the way."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you are one of the first 50,000 people to complete five pull requests, the Hacktoberfest project will send you a t-shirt!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Check out the complete participation details and rules over at the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com/details"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hacktoberfest site"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"why-celebrate-hacktoberfest-with-gatsby"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#why-celebrate-hacktoberfest-with-gatsby","ariaLabel":"why celebrate hacktoberfest with gatsby permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Why celebrate Hacktoberfest with Gatsby?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We couldn‚Äôt be more excited about Hacktoberfest ‚Äî it‚Äôs right up our alley! Back in August, we were excited to celebrate hitting 1,000 contributors! (As of this writing, it‚Äôs 1,197 üòÑ)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{"className":["twitter-tweet"],"dataLang":"en"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{"lang":"en","dir":"ltr"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We've hit 1000 contributors! Thank you for your trust and shared loved for what we're building together. "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://t.co/41j5fx9cF2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"pic.twitter.com/41j5fx9cF2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"‚Äî Gatsby (@gatsbyjs) "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/gatsbyjs/status/1027876829615595520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"August 10, 2018"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby is a great project to contribute to because you can learn about Gatsby while tackling a list of carefully curated issues, prepared especially for Hacktoberfest."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Our Hacktoberfest goals are:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To provide a range of issues with a clearly defined scope, with minimal background knowledge needed outside of the issue description."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To make contributing to Gatsby as welcoming, friendly, and accessible as we can ‚Äî especially to first-time contributors."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Plus, if you‚Äôve never contributed to Gatsby before, after your very first PR is merged, you can redeem some "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/contributor-swag/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"free Gatsby swag"}]},{"type":"text","value":"! ("},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Note: Not Hacktoberfest related. We do this always!"}]},{"type":"text","value":")"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"blockquote","properties":{"className":["twitter-tweet"],"dataLang":"en"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{"lang":"en","dir":"ltr"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Thanks "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/gatsbyjs?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@gatsbyjs"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for the t-shirt! If there are any developers out there that haven‚Äôt tried out Gatsby yet here is my dog Birch silently judging you. üòâ Trust me, it‚Äôs awesome. "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://t.co/THDSmhKdBb"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"pic.twitter.com/THDSmhKdBb"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"‚Äî Ryan Wiemer (@ryanwiemer) "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/ryanwiemer/status/1022267081998266368?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"July 25, 2018"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We so appreciate everyone who puts in the time to contribute to making Gatsby, and the whole open source community, even better üíú."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"how-do-first-time-contributors-get-started"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#how-do-first-time-contributors-get-started","ariaLabel":"how do first time contributors get started permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"How do first-time contributors get started?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Here are "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properti